L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FByAhVLL.jpg&h=b4fef7e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但鮮卑勢估唔到又會咁戲劇性, 岩岩先打去南方後蘭就比人捅一野...<br />\n長年既鬥爭於是就變左咁: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/whwPFpK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwhwPFpK.jpg&h=7ec920e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次應該冇問題la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088189210467c138ff866de663e4d9ab1ea2cc38","tid":1127696,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a281389fb0ce2564d0997236b9554afc84136ee","tid":1127696,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"tai長ng lun睇lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1cd9515af3c5ee2e67e0f0d94ff62cd5a0a947","tid":1127696,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"漢人係古代係指:「秦漢南遷同南方土著混血雜交出黎既大量混血漢二代.」<br />\n<br />\n秦漢時閩粵百越族人口已有200多萬<br />\n點混血百越族人始終係百越族人<br />\n漢族係指劉邦族人<br />\n大漢國人民稱為漢人<br />\n大唐國人民稱為唐人<br />\n近代閩粵被人屈做南漢人"},{"pid":"83f56c8b4e59464988a7d9ba46f63b12ed2d423c","tid":1127696,"uid":237496,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"088189210467c138ff866de663e4d9ab1ea2cc38","tid":1127696,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:00:29.000Z","msg":"滿清都係中原後裔, 八旗入面幾多古中原民族, <br />\n而且其他族裔都有貴族成員, 點解係得漢人mo份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;漢人最高係士族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以再睇返歷代中原稱皇稱帝ga大多數同漢人mo咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而漢人一路都係古今奴隸, <br